# Before making code change
- Do
    - given an outline of what your are planning to do.
    - ask for confirmation before proceeding
    - read naming-conventions

# After each code change
- Do
    - use pnpm and not npm
    - run `pnpm run type-check` in project root to check for any typescript errors
    - run `pnpm run lint` at project root to check for any linter errors
    - run `pnpm run build` at project root to check if build is successful
- Don't
    - Do not run the modules, they are already running in the background.

